Kia Pegg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kia_Pegg 0 Kia May Pegg (born 29 June 2000) is an English actress, who is most well known for her role as Jody Jackson in British children's drama show Tracy Beaker Returns (2012) and its follow-up The Dumping Ground (2013–). Jody is one of the longest running characters in the series. She has also been a guest star in the CBBC HQ and guest starred on Hacker Time and CBBC's Saturday Mashup.
